{"tid":1149752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚悚一瞬間！比特犬街上「暴衝亂咬」　郵差遭襲慘皮開肉綻","createTime":"2019-05-11T11:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T11:27:30.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f8b5c0b41d947b48fbd4047db5f37217216af9","tid":1149752,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-21ZPY_QLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-21ZPY_QLc&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=e50de64f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-21ZPY_QLc</a><br />\n<br />\n昨（10）日新竹市的馬路上發生驚悚的狗咬人事件，一名郵務士騎車行經信勢國小與成功路口的時候，一隻比特犬突然從旁邊的小貨車上面跳下來張口狂咬，郵務士儘管連忙起身拉住，但褲管已經被比特犬撕掉，腿部也出現大面積傷口。網友看到後都相當憤怒，表示「一定要告飼主！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LSh8bC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LSh8bC.jpg&h=d60e895d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywZTGwG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywZTGwG.jpg&h=03d7e7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有民眾昨日在臉書社團《我愛湖口鄉》PO出這段駭人影片，從畫面中可以清楚看見，比特犬的血盆大口狠狠咬住郵務士的褲管，褲子的膝蓋以下已經完全消失，即使主人使勁拉著比特犬，但牠還是不鬆口。而曾姓郵務士當下雖然出力想要把褲子拉回來，但險些又因此再度摔倒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUsqxDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUsqxDs.jpg&h=ac467605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n郵務士事後將受傷的照片分享在網路上，只見他的小腿遍佈各種傷口，鮮血也不斷從患部持續流出來，不少網友看到後留言表達對他的關心，「辛苦了，祝你早日康復！」「趕快到醫院打破傷風」、「先去醫院就醫，取得證明，可以求償，請郵局主管出面幫你討公道」、「咬很深欸，傷口要照顧好」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0WCoLd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0WCoLd.jpg&h=a01e2872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但也有人怒批主人養狗的方式很有問題，痛斥「希望派出所可以去關切這一家的狗主人」、「為什麼狗不綁要害人」、「 主人還在用手打，用腳踢比較快！捨不得打等咬的是小孩老人，出事了就拿命來還」、「狗主人帶狗出門前最好先想清楚（別再讓無辜路人受傷了）」、「抓主人判刑，蓄意謀殺」、「一定要告飼主」。"},{"pid":"87e8f630e77c453327802a351b7a20a6287e75b1","tid":1149752,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:12:50.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"d2de06dba6e2b657ea32c15c8aea5c764049ed9e","tid":1149752,"uid":213637,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"傻閪狗撚:狗狗係無辜 狗狗唔會亂咬人 一定係郵差挑釁"},{"pid":"157d6377dd12dd7d264afba1b4c55950ee574f46","tid":1149752,"uid":244243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e81c3f82f940bb944e1e38bcdb09a2f502f6457","tid":1149752,"uid":199162,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"狗界Nigga"},{"pid":"2e7d57557a042090218e21742e6f06117ddef37f","tid":1149752,"uid":237168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:25:26.000Z","msg":"又冇搞隻狗都冇啦啦咬尻人 <br />\n呢啲惡狗應該人道毀滅 <br />\n兼賠償一大筆"},{"pid":"1f57920f4f0c2a03c73ce35a1b4b48bff81760d1","tid":1149752,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"都話狗同中國人無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7556971582645c8c02a2ed90e251c676fe5447f7","tid":1149752,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e81c3f82f940bb944e1e38bcdb09a2f502f6457","tid":1149752,"uid":199162,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"狗界Nigga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"Nigga最鍾意養"}]}